:: ''attempt'' to blink. {"position":"2900,800","size":"100,100"}
You try your hardest to blink but it feels like your entire body is activley fighting against you, you want to see, you NEED to see.

The more your eyes gaze into the infinite the more you feel the surrounding area change and warp, you cant see it but you can "feel" it...

[[stamp your own foot]]
[[try to look away]]
[[try to look DEEPER]]


