:: Fifteen years? {"position":"3500,1700","size":"100,100"}
The man blinks a few times his smile never ceasing before he finally comes to his senses and responds back 
//OH my Apologies!!! I mean 15 minutes?//
He says, with a hint of confusion, you get the sense He.....it....dosent grasp time very well.



