:: Go to the Pirate door {"position":"3900,1800","size":"100,100"}
As you approach the door you notice the door didnt read "Pirate" after all, it said "Private".
obviously.
The door opens suprisingly easily, and swings open revealing a pitch black dark room, there are candles placed on the floor their flicker dont illuminate anything but themselves. 
You feel around for a lightswitch trying to see your surroundings, your hand glides along the wall skimming the different materials that plaster the wall, sandpaperish textures until your fingers get intertwined with a slimy substance, 


:: Greet the man behind the counter {"position":"3400,1300","size":"100,100"}
Stepping forward cautiously, you approach the smiling man behind the counter, he stares forward at you with bated breath.
//Hello! Welcome! Please please won't you have some of our delicious ramen!?//
The man looks like he's never been more excited for your answer. His chest breathing heavily you notice the material of his outfit a bit more now, like his [[buttons]].

[[No. Why the hell would i want your ramen! What are you doing to people?!]]

[[Stare blankly]]

[[Sure.]]

[[No thank you,]]


