:: No thank you, {"position":"3300,1500","size":"100,100"}
The mans shoulders slump a little hearing your response.
// Well, er, still feel free to browse our menu in case you change your mind! //
You nod and take a menu although you have Zero intention on eating here. 
[[Inside]]


:: No. Why the hell would i want your ramen! What are you doing to people?! {"position":"3100,1500","size":"100,100"}
You shout at the man behind the counter loudly forgetting where you are momentarily lost in the rage, feeling for the all the people that have gone missing and knowing this man has something to do with it and all he does is smile.
The restaraunt falls silent, noone is eating anymore.
theyre all...
(text-colour:red)[''Staring.'']

The man however is still [[smiling]] his face not having changed at all.



:: Q: Where do you get your ingredients? {"position":"4200,1400","size":"100,100"}



:: Q: Why do I keep thinking of worms? do you sell worms here? {"position":"4400,1400","size":"100,100"}



:: Q: Why do you smile like that? {"position":"4300,1400","size":"100,100"}



:: SNAP OUT OF IT! {"position":"3100,2300","size":"100,100"}
You blink rapidly and try to shake the thoughts away 

The mans head has contorted his jaw a gaping maw three times larger than his head his eyes have stretched and warped to the sides of his head, dozens of sets of teeth lay inside his mouth saliva connecting the roof of his mouth to his tounges, and to the tip of your nose. The form immedialty switches back to a somewhat human form seeing you snap out of it. 
//You will smile...dont worry...ill make you...//
he mutters still keeping his perfect smile, 
// S M I L E //
As he commands the entire restaruant says it with him perfectly synchronized.
// S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E S M I L E  // 
The room chants as his fingers press into where your mouth used to be and morphs it like clay pushing your cheek bones up so much you can feel the tears in your eyes form.
// You shall cook fine // 
The man says almost contemplatedly, 
before he reaches up and grabs his mouth tearing it off his skin blood gushing out, as he holds you down with suprising force, he delicatley places the blood soaked mouth onto your face, and---WMIFKEDNIGMO44###MIKJN@NBHn@u Nn$%NMNJML.V,,SASS

[[Feed]]


:: Stare blankly {"position":"3900,1500","size":"100,100"}
You blankly stare at the man unsure of what to say in response, his smile fades quickly and returns his attention to overseeing the cashiers and cooks, you glance over the counter and spy a door which looks like it reads as "Pirate" 

[[Get the cooks attention for questioning]]

[[Go to the Pirate door]]

[[Leave the restaraunt]]

[[Inside]]


:: Start [Beginning] {"position":"2700,0","size":"100,100"}
                                                                Ramen. 
                         
                         
                         
                        
You walk down the street signs for cheap ramen restaraunts are sprinkled through the streets, [[several missing posters]] that show the faces of mysteries.
You fix your [[Tie]] in nervousness, you can feel your forehead dripping with sweat, your lucky pen shifting around in your breast pocket. The weight of your notebook in your bag.


:: Struggle {"position":"3100,1900","size":"100,100"}
As you struggle and panic you manage to shake a ''few'' of them off in time but theres too many they crawl their hands around to your face their movements growing erratic and almost animalistic in their attempts to consume you.
But they don't.
They finish...whatever they were doing and simply all stare at you as you look up at them from the floor, the man from behind the counter's face slides into view seamlessly.
He's floating.
[[shit]]


:: Sure. {"position":"3500,1500","size":"100,100"}
//Wonderful! I shall get it prepared right away it should be done in fifteen years!!//
[[Fifteen years?]]


:: Take in the area of the entrance {"position":"3600,1100","size":"100,100"}
Looking around you observe the glass doors you opened to get in the red carpet with small blue diamonds covering the ground, a wooden counter with a smiling cook standing behind it staring at you expectantly. Ravenous customers in velvet booths and dining tables littered around the restaraunt, it looks jam packed full but somehow you feel like if you asked the staff would a find a seat for you.



:: This is good [Ending] {"position":"2900,1900","size":"100,100"}
This is good.
Your mouth is completely gone. 
Screaming only echoes inside your mind, tearing away at your face does nothing, you dont even see the cook glancing down at you.
you dont even notice his transformation and his gigantic jaw opening, you dont notice the end of everything, you dont notice the thousands of screams that plague your canals or the hot blood rising and falling from your eyes as they roll back, all you see is space, and him. Him. The worm. The Deity. The cleanser. The feeder. It feeds on planets like theyre nothing, eating them, as it should. as HE should. 
You Feel the coldness of your body.
You Barely feel your mind drifting on.
You scarcely feel you had to remember having memories.
You dont feel.

But....

you could go for some ramen right about now.

Ending 3


:: Tie [flavour-text] {"position":"2600,200","size":"100,100"}
Your dark black tie, its got navy blue stains around the top and always looks somewhat desheveled. 
You still rememeber the first day you got this tie, you had just bought your first apartment in Sakanua the rent was good and the location was snobby so you decided to buy a tie as a joke but liked how it looked.



:: You reach THE ramen store {"position":"3400,700","size":"100,100"}
Upon reaching the ramen store you can see the prices on a [[black chalkboard]] out front and the patrons inside stuffing theyre faces as much as they possibly can. 

You clutch your [[notebook]]

And head [[Inside]]




:: black chalkboard [flavour-text] {"position":"3600,500","size":"100,100"}
XL Ramen $4.00
Only thing sale.
come eat human food by humans.

*you feel a sense of....confusion?*
[[You reach THE ramen store]] 


:: buttons [flavour-text] {"position":"3100,1200","size":"100,100"}
Taking in his appearance you notice more and more strange things, 
for one the buttons on his bright white chef outfit are made out of wood. His black jet black hair having strands madded to his forehead, and his perfect white teeth. 
you are slowly starting to think this isnt a he...
but more of an it...


:: is there something in there? [goofed-up] {"position":"2700,800","size":"100,100"}
Oh yes. yes you see it now, theyre black hair falls in front of the void slightly obscuring it from your view, but you see "it" right? its so close! its right [[there!]] 


:: notebook [flavour-text Notebook-Entry] {"position":"3600,700","size":"100,100"}
Your notebook that contains all the evidence and theories pertaining to the people who go missing at this very ramen store. 
the newspaper clipping thats stuck onto one of the pages reads
"A new ramen shop has opened up! its located in the alleyway next to genji sha petrol station! *an image is stuck with a paperclip showing a giant line going from inside the ramen store to all the way across the petrol station* at the time of broadcast we have no information on who owns the store, where it came from, or how it cropped up seemingly overnight! All this reporter knows is that this ramen is to die for!

*you feel a sense of obvious foreshadowing*
[[You reach THE ramen store]] 


:: several missing posters [Important-choice] {"position":"2700,200","size":"100,100"}
The posters show the people you've been tracking down clues about for some time now, the oldest one has moss covering the corners of the poster, and there appears to be [[something on the oldest posters]] down the end of the wall? [[Ignore them, remain focused.]]


:: shit {"position":"3100,2100","size":"100,100"}
As you attempt to curse, you realize what they were doing as your hands dart aronud your face searching for it!
your mouth is gone.
There are no marks to ever suggest one was there in the first place, just a smooth surface and cheek bones stuck in static. You try to speak again and again and again but are met with nothing not a single word, 
//What was that? I couldn't hear you?//
The man behind you giggles as if he's just pulled a small prank. His hands come down to your face, stopping just short his hands cupping your cheeks, every bone in your body refusing to move you are rigid with fear, his eyes gaze deeply into yours until you notice his eyes, the iris, the insides, theres a worm, it devours planets like theyre nothing. spreading through space like a plauge unbeknownst to anyone, you see it snatch up your planet, your family, you.
[[SNAP OUT OF IT!]]



:: smiling {"position":"3100,1700","size":"100,100"}
As the silence gets louder you look around noticing everyone staring at you, the once ravenous customers stopping everything even the baby's crying has ceased it too stares, not a flicker of emotion lights any of their faces,
As you focus your gaze back on the man behind the counter you he--
''SLAM''
The door slams shut by itself.
